emotes.msg: Double-click on me to hear what I have to say.
Shoo, fly!
WaspWingGiven
These look like the Academy Blacksmith's bellows. You should take this over to him--he's been bellyaching ever since the Mosswarts stole them. He'll probably reward you, too.
You must have been fighting our Sparring Golems lately. Instructive, aren't they? I'll give this back to the Senior Guard for you.
Yes, you are certainly welcome here! Especially if you go kill those horrid Carpenter Wasps for me!
Ah, my studying days are over, my friend. You may have this back.
Ah, my studying days are over, my friend. You may have this back.

The Blacksmith's Oil of Rendering...looks like you've helped him with those Mosswarts that have been plaguing him lately. I don't know why they're so fond of his bellows though...maybe he should take them on as his apprentices!
The Academy Foreman guffaws loudly at the Blacksmith's expense.
If you pour this oil onto one of the Quartermaster's Training Weapons, I'm sure you'll be happy with the result.
This is one of the Training items forged by our Quartermaster. If you use the Oil of Rendering that I gave you on it, you'll find its powers will increase tremendously.
You've bought one of the Quartermaster's Training Weapons. It's a nice one! But try pouring the Blacksmith's Oil of Rendering on it--I'm sure you'll be happy with the result.

This is the key to the Quartermaster's workshop. You should pay him a visit! To unlock the door, double-click on the key, then double-clicking on the door.
RecruitSent
The Foreman is nearly hysterical with fear.
Haven't you heard? The Outer Courtyard is under attack! What are we going to do? You must report to the Senior Guard--he will know!
I heard that you successfully helped the Blacksmith regain his bellows. Good job--I have no idea how those Mosswarts strayed in here, but they certainly don't belong.
WaspWingDone

Now, you have already helped me enough, my friend--I'm sure from now on I'll be able to manage these Wasps on my own. Good luck in the rest of the Academy! Have you already completed your Academy Weapon? You should show it to the Senior Guard--I'm sure he'd be happy to see your progress! Good luck in the rest of the Academy!

You have already helped me enough, my friend--I'm sure from now on I'll be able to manage these Wasps on my own. You should now go visit the Academy Blacksmith around the corner--the Mosswarts have been stealing from him, and I'm sure he could use your help. Good luck in the rest of the Academy!
Thank you! You are surely doing your part to ensure that this Academy will thrive. Let me reward you with experience.
You should now go visit the Academy Blacksmith--the Mosswarts have been stealing from him, and I'm sure he could use your help. Good luck with the rest of the Academy!
OilGiven

Perhaps you can help me out as well. Quickly, Carpenter Wasps have infested my woodpile! There are so many of them--could you help me clear out a few? They are here through this door beside me. If you bring me one of their wings to prove that you have taken some of them out, I will surely reward you.
